						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone near the temple of Kallēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>Jōyidēva (Undated.)</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary and undated inscription refers to <hi rend="bold">Jōyidēva</hi> and seems to record the death of a hero (name lost), probably the son of a certain <hi rend="bold">Bōviya-Nāyaka,</hi> in a fight. As no other details are available, it is difficult to identify this Jōyidēva.</p>						

						</summary>
