<!--<h4>First Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī svasti samastaprasastisahitaṁ śrīmanumāhana<note n="414-1">Mistake for śrīmanumahā.</note>
<lb n="2"/>maṁḍaḷēsvara vujjēnīpuravarādhīśvara hanirvvara gaṁḍa maṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḍaḷikabhairavu jōyidēvana Avasaradali <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> haḷiya <unclear>kāḷe</unclear><note n="414-2">Read va.</note>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ga<unclear>da</unclear>li bōviyana yaka<unclear>na</unclear> maga <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> jaya<unclear>kē</unclear><note n="414-3">Read nā.</note>
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Panel.</h4>-->

<p>The writing is completely effaced and peeled off.</p>

